 dependency chart

Level     Step	              Required Dependency	      Output Created
0	        Add Photos	        Raw Files (.jpg, .tif)	  Camera Group
1	        Align Photos	      Level 0	                  Tie Points (Sparse Cloud)
2	        Optimize Alignment	Level 1 + (Markers/GPS)	  Refined Camera Calibration
3	        Build Depth Maps	  Level 1 or 2	            Depth Maps
4	        Build Point Cloud	  Level 3	                  Dense Point Cloud
5a	      Build Model (Mesh)	Level 3 OR Level 4	      3D Mesh
5b	      Build DEM	          Level 3 OR Level 4	      Elevation Model
6a	      Build Texture	      Level 5a	                Textured Model
6b	      Build Orthomosaic	  Level 5a OR Level 5b	    Orthomosaic (Map)
7	        Export Tiles/ZIP	  Level 6a or 6b	          Final Deliverables